headline: Canadian defined benefit pension plans show decreased funded levels in Q1: Aon
summary: Aon plc (NYSE: AON), a leading global professional services firm, announced today that the aggregate funded ratio for Canadian pension plans in the S&P/TSX Composite Index percent compared to 107.5 percent at the end of last quarter, according to the Aon Pension Risk Tracker.
